        <sponsor name-id="S332">Mr. Franken</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="S339">Mr. Kirk</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S311">Ms. Klobuchar</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSHR00">Committee on Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions</committee-name>
